  "2225870": {
    "name": "黎明前夜",
    "steam_appid": 2225870,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/f116cf19fa7d27b95b1c788eead17754.avif?t=1733366103\" width=620 height=200 /></span><br>《黎明前夜》是一款爽快射击的Rougelite游戏，在这座丧尸爆发的城市中，从尸潮中杀出一条血路，获得救援！<br>反馈与交流QQ群：675793341<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/d49e19d81407dfe1ac259be13765fe59.avif?t=1733366103\" width=379 height=80 /></span><br>面对不断汹涌的丧尸，拿起手中的武器杀出血路，解锁与购买升级，获得救援！随机地图，随机奖励，随机载具，每一局都带来末日生存的变化与战斗体验！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/d868a3500d990aaa68b9946aecf1a802.poster.avif?t=1733366103\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/d868a3500d990aaa68b9946aecf1a802.webm?t=1733366103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/d868a3500d990aaa68b9946aecf1a802.mp4?t=1733366103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/c1df32bf2687e92647d9e37d655fe458.avif?t=1733366103\" width=374 height=79 /></span><br>游戏中可以解锁特性迥异的角色与技能。根据他们的特性以及你的风格，找到专属于自己的战斗构筑！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/83f50d8c30e7f919c2efce3c725d34e5.poster.avif?t=1733366103\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/83f50d8c30e7f919c2efce3c725d34e5.webm?t=1733366103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/83f50d8c30e7f919c2efce3c725d34e5.mp4?t=1733366103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/6c99487c3eb5ff5c319f07f4495dde30.avif?t=1733366103\" width=402 height=76 /></span><br>驾驶载具，探索地图，发现意外的奖励与惊喜！你可以做一名游侠，或者干脆撞出一条血路！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/17c74acbb3458c24526e7e7ad884ceef.poster.avif?t=1733366103\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/17c74acbb3458c24526e7e7ad884ceef.webm?t=1733366103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/17c74acbb3458c24526e7e7ad884ceef.mp4?t=1733366103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/11b57dba89533cdb6459c0296ed4bf92.avif?t=1733366103\" width=350 height=76 /></span><br>· 超过50种丰富的局内升级!<br>· 无限广阔的地图与丰富的探索奖励！<br>· 可破坏的场景以及丰富的载具！<br>· 单局节奏自己掌握，轻度却爽快.<br>· 天赋系统与局内商店助你变强.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/7b32d1687b12d4697af348fd57bb5d66.poster.avif?t=1733366103\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/7b32d1687b12d4697af348fd57bb5d66.webm?t=1733366103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/7b32d1687b12d4697af348fd57bb5d66.mp4?t=1733366103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/47538fb2cea326822df403ea0c87a8b3.avif?t=1733366103\" width=350 height=76 /></span><br>四种游戏模式，尽情探险吧！<br>· 莱肯市：在传统的探索模式中找到信号塔得到救援！<br>· 莱肯市（生存）：努力在充满尸潮的城市中活下来吧！<br>· 母巢模式：进攻在城市中的母巢，阻止敌人的攻势！<br>· 守塔模式：保护好自己的安全屋，努力撑到救援的到来！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/43e87ac021ef3fd9b602ede991ae154c.poster.avif?t=1733366103\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/43e87ac021ef3fd9b602ede991ae154c.webm?t=1733366103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/43e87ac021ef3fd9b602ede991ae154c.mp4?t=1733366103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/97dbeb6d3577597372f49bfffb4ee00b.poster.avif?t=1733366103\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/97dbeb6d3577597372f49bfffb4ee00b.webm?t=1733366103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/97dbeb6d3577597372f49bfffb4ee00b.mp4?t=1733366103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/b6983beb37dcd5079dcf119ca556a8fa.poster.avif?t=1733366103\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/b6983beb37dcd5079dcf119ca556a8fa.webm?t=1733366103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225870/extras/b6983beb37dcd5079dcf119ca556a8fa.mp4?t=1733366103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
